"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly uses sns.lmplot within the FacetGrid.map() function. According to the seaborn documentation, lmplot is a figure-level function and should not be used within an axes-level function like FacetGrid.map(). Instead, sns.regplot, which is an axes-level function, should be used.\",\n  \"patch\": \"6c6\\n<\\tg.map(sns.lmplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\\n---\\n>\\tg.map(sns.regplot, 'total_bill', 'tip')\"\n}"